</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of the ring in a dream for Al-Nabulsi</span></h2>
<p>Imam Al-Nabulsi says, if you see in your dream that you found a ring, then this vision indicates that you will get <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-الكثير-من-المال-لابن-سيرين?page=1849" > a lot of money</a> soon, God willing, but if you see that you are wearing a ring made of silver, then this indicates that you will find an excellent job soon.<br/>If you see in your dream that you are wearing an iron ring, then this indicates a lot of livelihood, but after a lot of fatigue and effort.  If you see someone giving you a ring, then this indicates love and cooperation.  A single young man, and this means the <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-زواج-قريب-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=3121" > soon marriage</a>.<br/>Seeing the loss of the ring is one of the unfavorable visions and shows the many worries and problems in the life of the seer, while the loss of the ring for the married person indicates marital problems that may lead to divorce.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of the ring in a dream for <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a></span></h2>
<p>Seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الخاتم-في-المنام?page=838" > silver ring</a> on the right hand indicates her marriage, while seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الخاتم-في-المنام?page=838" > ring</a> inlaid with <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/الأحجار-الكريمة-في-المنام?page=924" > precious stones</a> indicates the presence of a relationship with a man of influence, prestige, and knowledge.<br/>Wearing the <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ارتداء-الخاتم-في-المنام?page=3821" > ring</a> on the right hand in a dream for an unmarried woman is evidence of her close relationship, but seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-خاتم-ذهب-في-المنام?page=985" > gold ring</a> in a dream indicates that she has no share with her life partner.<br/>Seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-فتاة-في-المنام?page=4046" > girl</a> who is not married wearing a ring on her right hand and breaking it in a dream is evidence of her engagement being broken off and her separation due to a lack of understanding between them.</p>
<p>Seeing the sale of the ring that an unmarried girl is wearing in a dream is evidence of her separation from her lover or fiancé.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
