</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-امرأة-في-المنام?page=864" > woman</a> who is married wearing a ring in a dream and her husband helps her put it on means pregnancy in the near future.</p>
<p>Wearing the <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ارتداء-الخاتم-في-المنام?page=3821" > ring</a> on the right hand in a married woman's dream indicates an abundance of wealth and the arrival of abundant kindness.</p>
<p>Losing the ring, or having it stolen, or disappearing from the married woman's right hand indicates that she left her husband or was divorced from him.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
