</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-امرأة-في-المنام?page=864" > woman</a> who is married wearing a ring in a dream may indicate her recovery from illness if she is sick.</p>
<p>Losing the <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-فقدان-الخاتم-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=41" > ring</a> that a man is wearing on his right hand is evidence of losing someone he loves, whether it be his father, mother, sisters, children, or wife.</p>
<p>Stealing someone's ring in a man's dream is evidence that he will get money or land, or marry his wife after her divorce.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
