</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>For a pregnant woman, wearing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-الخاتم-الذهبي-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=354" > gold ring</a> on her right hand means she will give birth to a baby girl.</p>
<p>Wearing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-لبس-الخاتم-في-المنام?page=1530" > silver ring</a> on the right hand of a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" > pregnant woman</a> is evidence of her giving birth to a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-طفل-ذكر-لابن-سيرين?page=627" > baby boy</a>.</p>
<p>Seeing a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-امرأة-في-المنام?page=864" > woman</a> who is pregnant wearing a ring inlaid with diamonds, rubies, and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/الأحجار-الكريمة-في-المنام?page=924" > precious stones</a> in a dream is evidence of the birth of a beautiful boy who will have a wonderful and generous future, God willing.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
