</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Washing the ring that a young man is wearing on his right hand in a dream indicates that the seer is walking in the path of piety and faith.</p>
<p>Wearing an <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-لبس-الخاتم-في-المنام?page=1530" > old ring</a> in a dream for a divorced woman may indicate her return to her ex-husband, and if the ring is made of gold, then it indicates her marriage to a respectable and noble man.<br/>As for wearing the <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-لبس-الخاتم-في-المنام?page=1530" > ring</a> on the left hand in a dream, according to the interpretation of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin</a>, it is a blessed vision if the seer appears happy.  This may indicate that an unmarried girl will marry a man who possesses the qualities she desires and hopes for in her life partner.<br/>Wearing a ring on her left hand for an unmarried girl, but she felt fear and awe, is evidence that she will marry a man of great status or who works in an important position in the state, not an ordinary man like the rest of the people. .<br/>Wearing an <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-لبس-الخاتم-في-المنام?page=1530" > iron ring</a> on her left hand in a dream for an unmarried girl means that she will marry a rich man, God willing.</p>
<p>To read a detailed interpretation of seeing a bump in your dream, from the link &gt;&gt; Interpretation of a bump in a dream.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
