<p>Some interpretation experts added that <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-شروق-الشمس-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=38" >sunrise</a> from the west is considered one of the very bad signs, because it is an unpleasant sign that the person will be exposed to a painful accident in his life, God forbid, or that one of his secrets will be revealed.  He falls under the threat of scandals and defamation of his reputation, evidenced by his ascent. The west realizes the seer's fear, and the existence of many negative obsessions and thoughts that negatively affect his life.</p>
