<p>The appearance of the bright and radiant sun in the house of a married woman symbolizes many good signs that prove her happy life and joy with her husband due to his appreciation for her and respect for her, which makes her feel satisfied and grateful to him.  If she sees her husband leaving the house at <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-شروق-الشمس-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=38" >sunrise</a>, she fears most people revealing a secret in front of her, and they are doing their best to hide it from her, but God Almighty will reveal his matter very soon.</p>
