<p>The <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-رؤية-الشمس-في-المنام-للنابلسي?page=3682" >vision of the sun</a> of the <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" >pregnant woman</a> means for her many different symbols and indicators, as <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-شروق-الشمس-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=38" >sunrise</a> from the east indicates that the pregnancy is going smoothly and that she will enjoy a period of calm and stability even if she is in the last months of pregnancy, so she should prepare for childbirth because the facilitator is approaching that day will be free of obstacles and complications by God's command.</p>
