<p>Whoever sees that he is in a house and has been imprisoned and the door is tightly closed in a dream, this indicates that he does good and gives charity, because he gives charity and his right and left hands do not know this gift. , or it indicates that he is in good health and that God increases his health and provides him with abundant wealth.</p>
<p>Whoever sees that he is living in a house that is not his own and does not know who owns that house in his dream, this indicates that he is in love and tenderness with his wife, and his wife trusts him greatly and has deep love for him.  So he lives happily with his wife.</p>
