<h2><span>Interpretation of buying a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-منزل-جديد?page=2853" > new house </a> in a dream</span></h2>
<p>Said <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> that the interpretation of dreaming of buying a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-منزل-جديد?page=2853" > new house </a> is that it shows the state of the person or the dreamer in the world and his fluctuations from one state to another.  He was rich or poor, so if he was poor, God made him rich, but if he was rich, this indicates the continuation of wealth and the continuation of good and lawful money, and perhaps it indicates relief from sorrows, worries and purity of heart from all this.  Made of iron, it shows the dreamer's longevity and his age.</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Said <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> that seeing buying a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-منزل-جديد?page=2853" > new house </a> for a single or married girl and for a pregnant woman is to show the woman's status who has the dream in the world.  Traits grow up and become a righteous person.  The married or pregnant woman sees that she has bought a house that is not full except for her need, this indicates the birth of a beautiful woman who respects her parents and obeys them.</p>
