<h2><span>Interpretation of a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-منزل-جديد?page=2853" > new house </a> in a dream for a pregnant woman</span></h2>
<p>If a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" > pregnant woman </a> sees in her dream that she is moving to a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-منزل-جديد?page=2853" > new house </a> , this means a lot of nourishment, and also indicates getting rid of pain and suffering if she suffers from pregnancy pains, and if she moves to a house, this indicates that the <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-طفل-ذكر-لابن-سيرين?page=627" > baby boy </a> , but if she moves to an apartment, this indicates that the newborn is female.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-منزل-جديد?page=2853" > new house </a> in a dream for a married woman</span></h2>
<p>If a married woman sees in a dream that she is moving to a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-منزل-جديد?page=2853" > new house </a> , this means that her life will change for the better, but if she sees that her husband has a house and she does not know his owner, this indicates that her husband is committing many sins.</p>
<p>The house is the safest refuge for man, where man resides and performs all the activities of his daily life.  Some people may see the house and house in a dream or dream, and they may want to interpret this dream, so we have presented the interpretation of this dream in this topic.</p>
